      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REEL INFRARED (1) comes off an average performance last start when sixth at this track over 460m behind Full Noise (26.43) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Tough to beat if on-song. MISS SOOKY (4) was well fancied last time and led throughout to score (28.60) at Bendigo in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 500m. Can make it two on the bounce. AUDACIOUS PADDY (2) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, a neck from the winner Jumbuk Wang Wang (28.97) at Sale. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expecting another good run. ELEVATE (3) can fill a top-three spot.",
